    {
      "id": 50300,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Agent Duration \u2014 P50 / P95 / P99",
      "description": "Histogram from harness_agent_duration_seconds_bucket. The harness duration is the full agent execution cycle, not per-LLM-call latency \u2014 for that, you need Loki/Tempo (Stage 3).",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 12
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum by (le, agent) (rate(harness_agent_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "p50 {{agent}}",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, agent) (rate(harness_agent_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "p95 {{agent}}",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (le, agent) (rate(harness_agent_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "p99 {{agent}}",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "right",
          "showLegend": true
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "mappings": [
            {
              "type": "special",
              "options": {
                "match": "null+nan",
                "result": {
                  "text": "\u2014",
                  "color": "text-secondary"
                }
              }
            }
          ],
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {
            "fillOpacity": 5,
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 50900,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Stage 3 \u2014 Deferred (Loki + Traces required)",
      "collapsed": true,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 20
      },
      "panels": [
        {
          "id": 50910,
          "type": "text",
          "title": "Stage 3 panel placeholders",
          "gridPos": {
            "h": 6,
            "w": 24,
            "x": 0,
            "y": 21
          },
          "options": {
            "mode": "markdown",
            "content": "These panels are deferred to Stage 3 (Loki + Tempo) per `docs/GRAFANA-REFACTOR.md` \u00a7 8.\n\n**Requires Loki:**\n\n- API errors by `status_code` (429 vs 5xx vs 529 segmentation)\n- API errors by `model`\n- API request P50/P95/P99 latency by model\n- `api_retries_exhausted` rate (terminal-failure signal)\n- MCP server connection failures by `server_name`\n- Internal errors / auth failures / compaction failures\n\n**Requires Traces beta (`CLAUDE_CODE_ENHANCED_TELEMETRY_BETA=1`):**\n\n- TTFT (time to first token) P50 / P95 by model \u2014 highest-value traces panel; add first when Tempo is deployed.\n- Average attempts per request (silent 2nd-attempt successes that `api_retries_exhausted` doesn't surface)."
          },
          "fieldConfig": {
            "defaults": {},
            "overrides": []
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
